import {
  Box,
  Button,
  Checkbox,
  Container,
  FormControlLabel,
  Grid,
  Link,
  Typography,
  
 } from '@mui/material';
 import React, { useState } from 'react';
 
 function Login() {
  return (
   <>
    <Container component="main" maxWidth="xs">
     <Box>
      <Typography component="h1" variant="h5">
       Sign In
      </Typography>
      <Box component="form">
       <TextField
         margin="normal"
         required
         fullWidth
         id="email"
         type="email"
         label="Email Address"
         name="email"        
         autoFocus
        />
        <TextField
         margin="normal"
         required
         fullWidth
         name="password"
         label="Password"
         type="password"
         id="password"
        />
       <FormControlLabel
        control={<Checkbox value="remember" color="primary" />}
        label="Remember me"
       />
       <Button
        type="submit"
        fullWidth
        variant="contained"
        sx={{ mt: 3, mb: 2 }}
        >
        Sign In
       </Button>
       <Grid>
        <Link href="">Forgot password?</Link>
       </Grid>    
       <Grid className="footer">
        <Typography component="h5">
         Don't have an account? <Link href="">Sign Up</Link>
        </Typography>
       </Grid>
      </Box>
     </Box>
    </Container>
   </>
  );
 }
 
 export default Login;
